5085 SystemZGenMCSubtargetInfo(const Triple &TT,
5086 StringRef CPU, StringRef TuneCPU, StringRef FS,
5087 ArrayRef<SubtargetFeatureKV> PF,
5088 ArrayRef<SubtargetSubTypeKV> PD,
5089 const MCWriteProcResEntry *WPR,
5090 const MCWriteLatencyEntry *WL,
5091 const MCReadAdvanceEntry *RA, const InstrStage *IS,
5092 const unsigned *OC, const unsigned *FP) :
5093 MCSubtargetInfo(TT, CPU, TuneCPU, FS, PF, PD,
5094 WPR, WL, RA, IS, OC, FP) { }

5097 const MCInst *MI, const MCInstrInfo *MCII,
5098 unsigned CPUID) const override {

5100 }
5101};

5120// ParseSubtargetFeatures - Parses features string setting specified
5121// subtarget options.
5122void llvm::SystemZSubtarget::ParseSubtargetFeatures(StringRef CPU, StringRef TuneCPU, StringRef FS) {
5123 LLVM_DEBUG(dbgs() << "\nFeatures:" << FS);
5124 LLVM_DEBUG(dbgs() << "\nCPU:" << CPU);
5125 LLVM_DEBUG(dbgs() << "\nTuneCPU:" << TuneCPU << "\n\n");
5126 InitMCProcessorInfo(CPU, TuneCPU, FS);
5127 const FeatureBitset &Bits = getFeatureBits();
5128 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureDFPPackedConversion]) HasDFPPackedConversion = true;
5129 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureDFPZonedConversion]) HasDFPZonedConversion = true;
5130 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureDeflateConversion]) HasDeflateConversion = true;
5131 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureDistinctOps]) HasDistinctOps = true;
5132 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureEnhancedDAT2]) HasEnhancedDAT2 = true;
5133 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureEnhancedSort]) HasEnhancedSort = true;
5134 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureExecutionHint]) HasExecutionHint = true;
5135 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureFPExtension]) HasFPExtension = true;
5136 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureFastSerialization]) HasFastSerialization = true;
5137 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureGuardedStorage]) HasGuardedStorage = true;
5138 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureHighWord]) HasHighWord = true;
5139 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureInsertReferenceBitsMultiple]) HasInsertReferenceBitsMultiple = true;
5140 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureInterlockedAccess1]) HasInterlockedAccess1 = true;
5141 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureLoadAndTrap]) HasLoadAndTrap = true;
5142 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureLoadAndZeroRightmostByte]) HasLoadAndZeroRightmostByte = true;
5143 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureLoadStoreOnCond]) HasLoadStoreOnCond = true;
5144 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureLoadStoreOnCond2]) HasLoadStoreOnCond2 = true;
5145 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureMessageSecurityAssist3]) HasMessageSecurityAssist3 = true;
5146 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureMessageSecurityAssist4]) HasMessageSecurityAssist4 = true;
5147 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureMessageSecurityAssist5]) HasMessageSecurityAssist5 = true;
5148 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureMessageSecurityAssist7]) HasMessageSecurityAssist7 = true;
5149 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureMessageSecurityAssist8]) HasMessageSecurityAssist8 = true;
5150 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureMessageSecurityAssist9]) HasMessageSecurityAssist9 = true;
5151 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureMiscellaneousExtensions]) HasMiscellaneousExtensions = true;
5152 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureMiscellaneousExtensions2]) HasMiscellaneousExtensions2 = true;
5153 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeatureMiscellaneousExtensions3]) HasMiscellaneousExtensions3 = true;
5154 if (Bits[SystemZ::FeaturePopulationCount]) HasPopulationCount = true;
